<!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC "-//IETF//DTD HTML//EN">
<html>

<head>
 <title>Active Desktop 保护方式</title>
 <meta http-equiv="PICS-Label"   content="(PICS-1.1 &quot;http://www.rsac.org/ratingsv01.html&quot; l gen true comment &quot;RSACi North America Server&quot; by &quot;inet@microsoft.com&quot; for &quot;res://ie4tour.dll/welcome.htm&quot; on &quot;1997.06.30T14:21-0500&quot; r (n 0 s 0 v 0 l 0))"></meta>
 <meta http-equiv="content-type" content="text/html; charset=gb2312"></meta>
</head>

<style>
    body    { background : white; color : black; margin: 0 }
    body    { font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt}
    table   { font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; line-height: 12pt;}
    
    div.Offscreen     { display:none }
    span.Offscreen    { display:none }
    span.BulletNumber { font-size: x-large; font-weight: bold; color: #FF6600 }
    span.BulletText   { font-size: x-small; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: -1pt; text-align:center}
</style>

<body scroll=no>
 
<TABLE width=100% height=95% border=0 CELLPADDING=0 CELLSPACING=0>
<TR>
	<TD width=200>
	</TD>
	<TD valign=top>
	<span style="position:		relative; 
				 left:			+20; 
				 top:			+15;
				 margin-right:	+40; 
				 width:			90%;
				 ">
	<font style="font-family:	宋体; 
				 font-size:		30; 
				 font-weight:	bold; 
				 line-height:	24pt;
				 color:			#0099FF">
	Active Desktop 还原</font>
	<BR><BR>
	Internet Explorer 出现错误。为保险起见，Active Desktop 已暂时关闭。 如要重新启动 Active Desktop，请使用下面的疑难解答提示:
	<BR><BR>
	<table width=100% border=0 cellpadding=0 cellspacing=0>
	<TR>
		<TD VALIGN=TOP align=left>
			<span style="font-size: 100pt; 
						 position:	relative;
						 top:		69px;
						 left:		-4px;
						 font-family: Times, serif; 
						 color: #FF6600">&middot;</span>
		</TD>
		<TD>
			<object id="suih" width=0 height=0 classid="clsid:64AB4BB7-111E-11d1-8F79-00C04FC2FBE1">
			</object>
			浏览器是否已停止工作，或者您是否在未关闭系统的情况下重新启动了计算机? 如果是，请单击<a href="" target="_self" onClick="suih.ResetSafeMode();return false;">还原 Active Desktop</a>。<BR><BR>
		</TD>
	</TR>
	<TR>
		<TD VALIGN=TOP align=left>
			<span style="font-size: 100pt; 
						 position:	relative;
						 top:		69px;
						 left:		-4px;
						 font-family: Times, serif; 
						 color: #FF6600">&middot;</span>
		</TD>
		<TD VALIGN=TOP>
			您最近是否曾将新的项目添加到 Active Desktop 中？如果已添加，请尝试以下操作:
			<BR><BR>
			<ol>
			<li> 单击 <b>开始</b> 按钮，选择 <b>设置</b>，指向 <b>Active Desktop</b>，然后单击<b>自定义我的桌面</b>。
			<li> 清除新添加项目的复选框。
			</ol>
		</TD>
	</TR>
	<TR>
		<TD VALIGN=TOP align=left>
			<span style="font-size: 100pt; 
						 position:	relative;
						 left:		-4px;
						 top:		69px;
						 font-family: Times, serif; 
						 color: #FF6600">&middot;</span>
		</TD>
		<TD>
			是否关闭 Active Desktop 并恢复墙纸? 如果是，请单击 <b>开始</b> 按钮，选择 <b>设置</b>，指向 <b>Active Desktop</b>，然后单击 <b>按 Web 页查看</b>以便删除复选标记。
		</TD>
	</TR>
	</TABLE>

	</span>
	</TD>
</TR>
</TABLE>
</body>
</HTML>
